# Nexus API
### All API calls start with 

<pre class="base">
https://nexus.api.globusonline.org/
</pre>


### Format

All calls are returned in ***JSON***

# Users

## GET /users

Retrieves the user object.

#### example request

    $ curl https://nexus.api.globusonline.org/users/trhowe

#### response

    {
      "username": "trhowe"
    }


